			- Hand in the eggs to finish quest A.
		B: TM trainer asks you to see a farmer about a grown tickle tentacle.
			- Players can ask TM trainer about it, and find out that unless the tickle tentacles are captured, they may grown larger and unruly.
			- Talk to farmer in <???>, he says it was bigger than normal, almost like one of the arena bosses. He locked it in his shed.
			- Go to shed and fight a miniboss, loot corrupted tentacle and bring it back to TM trainer.
		C: The tentacle has been infused with corrupting magic. He tells you to ask around in town if someone has seen something sus.
			- One of the farmers will say he's heard strange noises from the derelict mine in the north east fields.
			- Go through the cave and kill a cultist trying to raise tentacle monsters.
			- Take out the cultists and bring back evidence to TM trainer.
			- Players unlock the armor set.

(test)  - Monk: Healer - Heals by attacking
Trainer: Portswood glade.
