	- Quest: Learning the ways of the monk:
		A: Inner focus:
			- Enter a glade area behind her house to find silkfiend nests.
				- Silkfiend: A new monster. A mobile pitcher plant (think pokemon) with vine legs and arms.
			- Bring the gong back and hand it in to start a test of tranquility. Basically just a challenge where you have to do splits while maintaining focus.
			- <monk> will do stuff to you while you maintain focus.
			- Once you complete the RP, you can hand in the quest.
		B: You are tasked to track down the whereabouts of Rotti, a dirty rattani fighter.
			- There's an underground fighting ring below the borm tavern.
			- Go there and talk to the boss, he'll tell you he'll give you Rotti's whereabouts if you defeat his champion.
			- Go into the ring and fight <miniboss>.
			- Once you win, talk to the boss. He'll give you an encoded letter and ask you to see <npc> in the sewers.
			- <npc> will translate it based on your gender and clothes:
				- breasts: put a recording crystal in your upper body armor while he transcribes it
				- penis: put a recording crystal in your lower body armor while he transcribes it
				- any: Pay 1 plat.
			- once translated, head back to <monk> for your reward
		C: You are sent to fight Rotti (female rattani) in a new dungeon. When you defeat her, she says <monk> and her spar every Tuesday. 
			And have this exchange going where Rotti gets to record each fight. <monk> always wins but seems to enjoy the dirty fighting.
			She says the gesture to prove that you were succesfful is to twist <monk>'s nipples.
			Go do that to finish the quest and unlock the armor.

